---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="SocialProof for Florists — Reviews That Fill Your Order Book | SocialProof">
  <main class="for-page">
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="badge">For Florists</div>
      <h1>Turn Beautiful Arrangements Into Beautiful Reviews</h1>
      <p class="subhead">Every wedding bouquet, sympathy arrangement, and anniversary delivery is a chance for a glowing testimonial. Vouch makes it effortless to collect and display them — right on your website.</p>
      <div class="cta-group">
        <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/signup" class="btn-primary">Start free — no credit card</a>
        <a href="/for" class="btn-secondary">See all industries →</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="pain">
      <h2>The Review Problem Florists Know Too Well</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Brides are thrilled on their wedding day — then life takes over and the review never happens</li>
        <li>Sympathy orders get deeply appreciated feedback that never makes it online</li>
        <li>You're competing with grocery store floral departments on Google — and your reviews need to prove you're worth the premium</li>
        <li>Seasonal rushes (Valentine's Day, Mother's Day) bring your best customers, but zero time to chase testimonials</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="solution">
      <h2>How Vouch Works for Florists</h2>
      <ol>
        <li><strong>Send a collect link</strong> — include it on your order confirmation, delivery card, or follow-up text</li>
        <li><strong>Customer fills a quick form</strong> — name, a few sentences, optional photo of their arrangement</li>
        <li><strong>You approve it</strong> — curate only what represents your brand beautifully</li>
        <li><strong>It embeds on your site</strong> — one script tag, works on any website builder</li>
      </ol>
      <p>No app download. No account needed from your customers. Takes them 60 seconds.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="social-proof-for-sp">
      <h2>What Florists Say About Vouch</h2>
      <blockquote>
        <p>"I added a collect link to my order confirmation emails. Within a week I had 12 new testimonials — more than I'd collected in the previous year."</p>
        <cite>— Floral studio owner, Portland OR</cite>
      </blockquote>
      <blockquote>
        <p>"Wedding clients love sharing their bouquet photos. Vouch makes it easy for them to attach a photo to their review. My gallery page has never looked better."</p>
        <cite>— Wedding florist, Nashville TN</cite>
      </blockquote>
    </section>

    <section class="use-cases">
      <h2>Perfect for Every Floral Business</h2>
      <div class="grid-3">
        <div class="card"><strong>Wedding florists</strong><p>Collect testimonials and bouquet photos from brides. Display them on your weddings gallery page to convert more inquiries.</p></div>
        <div class="card"><strong>Event florists</strong><p>Corporate clients and event planners trust you with their reputation. Let their words say so on your site.</p></div>
        <div class="card"><strong>Retail flower shops</strong><p>Turn repeat customers into a chorus of endorsements. Show locals why you beat the grocery store every time.</p></div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="faq">
      <h2>Common Questions</h2>
      <details>
        <summary>How do I send the collect link?</summary>
        <p>Paste it in your order confirmation email, print it on a delivery card with a QR code, or add it to your post-delivery text message. Your unique link is always the same — create it once, use it everywhere.</p>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>Can customers attach photos of their flowers?</summary>
        <p>Yes — the collect form includes an optional photo upload. Showcase the actual arrangements your customers loved.</p>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>What does it cost?</summary>
        <p>Free forever for 1 active widget — collect unlimited testimonials, display them on your site. Upgrade to Pro ($19/mo) for multiple widgets, advanced styling, and more.</p>
      </details>
    </section>

    <section class="final-cta">
      <h2>Ready to Let Your Customers Do the Selling?</h2>
      <p>Set up your first testimonial widget in minutes. Free forever for 1 active widget.</p>
      <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/signup" class="btn-primary">Get started free</a>
    </section>
  </main>

<div class="footer-links" style="margin-top:2rem;padding-top:1.5rem;border-top:1px solid #e5e7eb;font-size:0.9rem;">
  <strong style="color:#374151;">Also explore:</strong>
  <a href="/for/coaches" style="display:inline-block;margin:0.3rem 0.5rem 0.3rem 0;color:#2563eb;text-decoration:none;">For Coaches</a>
  <a href="/for/freelancers" style="display:inline-block;margin:0.3rem 0.5rem 0.3rem 0;color:#2563eb;text-decoration:none;">For Freelancers</a>
  <a href="/for/restaurants" style="display:inline-block;margin:0.3rem 0.5rem 0.3rem 0;color:#2563eb;text-decoration:none;">For Restaurants</a>
  <a href="/vs/senja" style="display:inline-block;margin:0.3rem 0.5rem 0.3rem 0;color:#2563eb;text-decoration:none;">vs Senja</a>
  <a href="/vs/testimonial" style="display:inline-block;margin:0.3rem 0.5rem 0.3rem 0;color:#2563eb;text-decoration:none;">vs Testimonial.to</a>
</div>
</Base>
